App Name: TikBooster - Followers & Likes

Brief:

TikBooster is designed to enhance the reach and popularity of TikTok content creators by facilitating connections among them. With this community-driven approach, TikTokers can amplify their presence by boosting their profiles to attract more followers, likes, and video views. This isn't a shortcut to instant fame; instead, it offers a way to be discovered by fellow users worldwide who may genuinely appreciate your content.
